-of-mistria-guides/444802/complete-fish-list-in-fields-of-mistria\"><strong>fish</strong></a>, <strong>flora</strong>, and <a href=\"https://www.polygon.com/e/444982\"><strong>insects</strong></a>. All of these collectables can be tracked in your in-game almanac <em>and</em> you can check the", "id": 1554451, "language": null, "link": "https://www.polygon.com/fields-of-mistria-guides/445259/museum-list-sections-archaeology-dig-spots", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 27, "page_rating_contents": 85, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source__id": 258, "source_url": "https://www.polygon.com/rss/index.xml", "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": null, "title": "Fields of Mistria museum collectables list", "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-11-20T16:10:52+00:00", "description": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<figure>\n\n<img alt=\"\" data-caption=\"\" data-portal-copyright=\"\" data-has-syndication-rights=\"1\" src=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/chorus/uploads/chorus_asset/file/25425864/lymynr1s.png?quality=90&#038;strip=all&#038;crop=0,0,100,100\" />\n\t<figcaption></figcaption>\n</figure>\n<p class=\"has-text-align-none\">Similar to many Humble Bundles we\u2019ve featured in the past, <a href=\"https://www.fanatical.com/en/fantasyverse\">Fanatical has started offering books</a> alongside its selection of gaming bundles. To mark the occasion, through Nov. 24, Polygon readers can save an extra 7% on Fanatical book bundles by using the code <strong>FANTASYVERSE7</strong> at checkout.</p>\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-none\">Fanatical is already offering a broad selection of books as part of these bundles, including classic issues from <a href=\"https://www.fanatical.com/en/bundle/classic-gems-by-dark-horse-comic-bundle\">Dark Horse Comics</a>, <a href=\"https://www.fanatica", "id": 1554060, "language": null, 